<!-- TERMS -->
<h2 id="terms">Terms &amp; Conditions</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Guests must be 18 years or older to make a reservation.</li>
  <li>A valid government-issued photo ID is required at check-in.</li>
  <li>Full payment is required at the time of booking.</li>
  <li>Free cancellation is available up to 48 hours before check-in.</li>
  <li>Cancellations within 48 hours of check-in will incur a 1-night charge.</li>
  <li>Check-in time is 2:00 PM. Early check-in is subject to availability.</li>
  <li>Check-out time is 12:00 PM. Late check-out may be requested for an additional charge.</li>
